Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}その合図で───
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:52.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}願うならフィクション　スローモーション
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:14:00.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}そして始まる　鮮やかな温もりと　残像が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:06.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}誰かの明日を　護るなら　戦士気取って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:13.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}悔しさと　悲しみで　恐怖を断ち切れ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:19.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}命のパラドックス　神のアルゴリズム
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:26.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2\fad(0,500)}戦略は　追い込まれ　笑っちゃうね
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.34,0:13:17.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}時過境遷  多想要留念你的話語
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.31,0:13:23.36,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}旅途的便簽  隨手的塗鴉也變得珍貴
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.36,0:13:26.53,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}描繪又擦除  就要四分五裂
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.53,0:13:32.41,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}夢醒的代價  白日夢的戲法
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.41,0:13:35.87,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}迷失於未知
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.87,0:13:38.62,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}被月光點亮
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.62,0:13:41.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}映照出你的影子
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.67,0:13:45.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}那輪廓微微擺動
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}開始的信號───
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.42,0:13:52.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}若如你所願  不過是虛構與慢動作
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.18,0:14:00.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}伴隨著鮮明的溫熱和殘影  一切起始
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.77,0:14:06.94,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}想要守護誰的未來  自居為戰士
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.94,0:14:13.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}以悔恨與悲傷淹沒恐懼
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.49,0:14:19.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2}生命的悖論  神明的算法
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.08,0:14:26.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2\fad(0,500)}當戰略陷入絕境  何不笑而面對
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:23.69,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}潮風に溶けた面影は幻のままで今も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:31.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}リアルで鮮明な思い出は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:36.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}何度も何度も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:44.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}嘘でもいいからそばにいてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.33,0:22:49.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}もっと近くで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:54.76,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}すぐ好きになって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:57.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}時間だけが過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:03.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}あぁ…戻りたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.27,0:23:12.28,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}失恋ソング沢山聴いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:19.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}泣いてばかりの私はもう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.95,0:23:22.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}捨てたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:25.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}強がらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:30.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}素直になってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:37.68,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}お願いあの日の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:43.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}あきらめないで傷付いても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:48.72,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}どうかその手を離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:50.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}離さないでよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.97,0:23:55.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}なんて遅いよね
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.97,0:22:23.69,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}你的面容隨海風飄散彷如幻影
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.98,0:22:31.53,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}可記憶卻如此鮮明難以忘卻
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.53,0:22:36.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}一次又一次反覆
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.87,0:22:44.33,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}請待在我身邊 謊言也無妨
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.33,0:22:49.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}再近一些
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.55,0:22:54.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}就這樣陷入愛河
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.76,0:22:57.55,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}只剩時間流逝
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.55,0:23:03.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}想要回歸
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.27,0:23:12.28,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}聽過太多失戀的歌
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.99,0:23:19.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}總是哭泣的我
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.95,0:23:22.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}也想要不管不顧
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.16,0:23:25.92,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}不必逞強
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.92,0:23:30.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}坦率一些
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.00,0:23:37.68,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}向那天的我許願
Dialogue: 1,0:23:39.42,0:23:43.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}不要放棄 哪怕受傷
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.20,0:23:48.72,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}不要放開緊握的手
Dialogue: 1,0:23:48.72,0:23:50.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}不要放開。
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.97,0:23:55.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord1\fad(300,300)}卻為時已晚
